Class
Description
Command
Command objects represent commands/user actions sent from the UI to the model.
Command.CancellationCode
Enumerate cancellation code options
Command.CommandValue
Enumerate possible types of command
Command.FeedbackCode
Enumerate feedback code options
Command.ResolutionCode
Enumerate resolution code options
CommandTest
Glass box unit tests for the command class.
IoTest
Glass box unit tests for TicketReader and TicketWriter classes.
Ticket
Ticket object represents a single filed ticket containing information about a specific issue/request.
Ticket.Category
Options for ticket category
Ticket.Priority
options for ticket priority
Ticket.TicketType
options for ticket type
TicketList
Maintains a list of tickets.
TicketListTest
Glass Box Unit Tests for TicketList
TicketManager
Concrete class that maintains the 'TicketList' and handles 'Commands' from the GUI.
TicketManagerGUI
Container for the TicketManager that has the menu options for new ticket tracking files, loading existing files, saving files and quitting.
TicketManagerTest
Glass Box Unit Tests for TicketManager
TicketReader
The TicketReader class provides static methods for reading tickets from a text file.
TicketState
Interface for states in the Ticket Manager State Pattern.
TicketTest
Glass box unit tests for the Ticket class.
TicketWriter
TicketWriter provides static methods for writing lists of tickets to text files for storage.
